{"tid":1980921,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[黃到發金] 葵廣小店成功申請送飯比坐監手足，先前己出錢買葵廣電梯廣告位做連儂牆","createTime":"2020-04-20T11:21:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-25T16:58:13.000Z","uid":38744,"like":116,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":47,"replies":[{"pid":"cb3179b1f149e58afe1f1205ec107e544e62d56d","tid":1980921,"uid":38744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T11:21:17.000Z","msg":"幫幫蘋果click一click一入去先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200420/JBQ4KUKNQL7AH25ZARHCAPQMBE/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR2165-u9WdZwaZU5G-R5xrfUPvU11Syp_N02iOzZb_4JEW4g2C7A9-i7To\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200420%2FJBQ4KUKNQL7AH25ZARHCAPQMBE%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR2165-u9WdZwaZU5G-R5xrfUPvU11Syp_N02iOzZb_4JEW4g2C7A9-i7To&d=Sy1M3c%2BVV8kZ1V6TqBoGPlpzQI%2FFghXCkDWT3grjsfs%3D&h=6bce3c60\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200420%2FJBQ4KUKNQL7AH25ZARHCAPQMBE%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR2165-u9WdZwaZU5G-R5xrfUPvU11Syp_N02iOzZb_4JEW4g2C7A9-i7To&h=7657b6b5\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200420/JBQ4KUKNQL7AH25ZARHCAPQMBE/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR2165-u9WdZwaZU5G-R5xrfUPvU11Syp_N02iOzZb_4JEW4g2C7A9-i7To</a><br />\n節錄：<br />\n葵涌廣場一間小食店<span style=\"color: red;\">一月</span>底遞表，四月中成功申請做勵敬懲教所的首間供應商。<br />\n<br />\n他回憶入獄的第一天便吃到那條傳說中的炸魚，當晚更不適至噴射式嘔吐，「因為條魚冇清內臟就炸，而且用萬年油，就算捱得過嗰個腥，食完都會成身生火瘡。」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n獲悉申請成功後，Nic坦言心情複雜，「見到有私家飯成百幾蚊一個火腩飯，我哋就定價每餐50蚊左右，希望易啲負擔得到，其實最好就唔使做呢啲餐，但係一日有濫捕有手足還押，都需要有人去做。」食店同時亦申請成為荔枝角及壁屋懲教所的供應商，正候審批。據悉，有其他食店亦在嘗試申請做供應商。<br />\n<br />\n間野反送中果陣一早已經租左落球場果邊個3樓電梯既黃金廣告位比人做連儂牆<br />\n然後依家一月又一早申請做供應商送飯比手足<br />\n真係出錢又出力<br />\n黃撚到發金<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2170e8090158a9f7fb4fccc7fcc10e0b25c01c0f","tid":1980921,"uid":345502,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"cb3179b1f149e58afe1f1205ec107e544e62d56d","tid":1980921,"uid":38744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T11:21:17.000Z","msg":"幫幫蘋果click一click一入去先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200420/JBQ4KUKNQL7AH25ZARHCAPQMBE/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR2165-u9WdZwaZU5G-R5xrfUPvU11Syp_N02iOzZb_4JEW4g2C7A9-i7To\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200420%2FJBQ4KUKNQL7AH25ZARHCAPQMBE%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR2165-u9WdZwaZU5G-R5xrfUPvU11Syp_N02iOzZb_4JEW4g2C7A9-i7To&d=Sy1M3c%2BVV8kZ1V6TqBoGPlpzQI%2FFghXCkDWT3grjsfs%3D&h=6bce3c60\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200420%2FJBQ4KUKNQL7AH25ZARHCAPQMBE%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR2165-u9WdZwaZU5G-R5xrfUPvU11Syp_N02iOzZb_4JEW4g2C7A9-i7To&h=7657b6b5\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200420/JBQ4KUKNQL7AH25ZARHCAPQMBE/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR2165-u9WdZwaZU5G-R5xrfUPvU11Syp_N02iOzZb_4JEW4g2C7A9-i7To</a><br />\n節錄：<br />\n葵涌廣場一間小食店<span style=\"color: red;\">一月</span>底遞表，四月中成功申請做勵敬懲教所的首間供應商。<br />\n<br />\n他回憶入獄